content: lalalune: Made a foundational contribution to the `jeju` repository, merging a massive pull request that introduced new applications (elizaos/jeju#1, +71k/-25k lines). In addition to this core delivery, they planned future development by opening issues for new agents and load testing (jeju#2, jeju#3, jeju#4) and identified a build issue in the `eliza` repository (elizaos/eliza#5673). Their code changes indicate this effort involved a significant mix of refactoring and testing work.
